payment flow
[User Clicks Pay]
        ↓
[Frontend Sends Checkout to Backend]
        ↓
[Backend Creates Razorpay Order]
        ↓
[Frontend Opens Razorpay Checkout]
        ↓
[User Pays]
        ↓
[Success Handler Fires]
        ↓
[Backend Updates Order as Paid]
        ↓
[Razorpay Settles ₹ to Your Bank]
